fields.content: Updates: Kzohh is blind indeed. Nothing can help him regain sight. The reason was trauma. However, he was declared completely healthy and happy in all other ways.
He's been active lately, and participated in social rat life.

fields.title: Vortex successfully healed!
fields.content: A black rat, named Vortex, has had a tumor removed. It appeared that, at that moment, only one clinic in Kyiv, called Exovet, had a rattologist. Now, Vortex has already recovered, and only sports a shaved spot with a scar on his back.

fields.title: Galder marries Nagash
fields.content: Two male rats, Galder (a damboid) and Nagash (a classical rat) have formed a couple. Interestingly, rats seemingly don't have the notion of monogamy, since they attempt to fuck other rats too, and neither feels jealous.

fields.title: What's up with Kzohh's eyes?
fields.content: Previously, Kzohh (a silver damboid rat) has lost his eye in a fight. He had a surgery to remove the remains, as they could be infected. Now, his other eye has become red, without a pupil, and he seems to be totally blind. Today Kzohh visits a doctor, but we suspect he will remain blind. However, sight is a very secondary sense with rats, as they mostly rely on smells and whiskers, and Kzohh's life quality does not seem to be impaired. The illness is probably caused by bad bloodline, as his brother Kanwulf (rest in peace) had sick eyes, too.
